@@ -0,0 +1,43 @@
+# Phase 2.19 — Route Incident RCA Persistence + Quality/Usefulness Feedback
+
+## Цель
+Дать route-governance RCA такой же governance-контур, как:
+- обычному `operator_rca`
+- `routing incident RCA`
+
+## Компоненты
+- `operator_routing_incident_route_rca_results_persister_v2_19.py`
+- `operator_routing_incident_route_rca_quality_scorer_v2_19.py`
+- `operator_routing_incident_route_rca_feedback_loop_v2_19.py`
+
+## Потоки
+- input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_results`
+- quality input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_quality`
+- quality result: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_quality_results`
+- feedback input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_feedback`
+- feedback summary: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_feedback_summary`
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_quality_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_feedback_summary + - COUNT 3
+curl -s localhost:9902/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_results_'
+curl -s localhost:9903/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_quality_'
+curl -s localhost:9904/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_feedback_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- feedback advisory-only
